|--------|-------------------|----------------------|
| **Purpose** | High-level summary | Detailed execution results |
| **Scope** | All user stories in Epic | Single test execution |
| **Audience** | Management, stakeholders | QA engineers, developers |
| **Update Frequency** | After each US Phase 4 | After EVERY E2E run |
| **File Location** | `docs/test-results/epic-01/E2E_TEST_REPORT.html` | `playwright-report/index.html` |
| **Archive Location** | Single file, updated | `cycle-X-timestamp/playwright-report/` |
| **Content** | Pass/fail summary, achievements, next steps | Detailed traces, screenshots, videos |
| **Creation** | Manual (update existing) | Automatic (Playwright generates) |
| **Review** | Quick overview | Deep dive debugging |
| **Screenshots** | None | Yes (failures, optional all steps) |
| **Videos** | None | Optional |
| **Interactivity** | Static HTML/CSS | Interactive (click traces, watch videos) |

